      "author": "davidvkimball",
      "description": "### New Features\r\n* **Footer Text:** Add configurable footer text displayed on all non-title slides\r\n* **Slide Numbers:** Add optional slide numbers with your choice of bottom-left or bottom-right positioning\r\n* **Auto-Fit:** Add an optional auto-fit toggle to automatically shrink overflowing vertical slide content so it fits cleanly in the viewport\r\n\r\n### Fixes & Improvements\r\n* Improved slide number positioning to maintain consistent alignment with footer text and the progress bar\r\n* Fixed an issue where the auto-fit zoom scale would jarringly reset during slide transitions\r\n* Ensured accurate slide numbering behavior and visibility when using vertical slide stacks\r\n\r\nThanks to @are-scenic for PR #5 and contributing these features.\r\n",
